creator: Vikkoo
descriptionHtml:
The word “VIKKOO” in colloquial south Indian language of Malayalam means to “sell” and this is the core spirit of this platform. VIKKOO.COM is designed to be an online platform to help home chefs ignite their creative passions by being able to market and sell their culinary magic to customers with an adventurous palate.

Customers hungry for tasty homemade delicacies can download our mobile app to browse and place orders of scrumptious creations from our home chefs.

Quality homemade food delivered to your doorstep safely and efficiently. All you need to do now is open the packet and enjoy the aroma of delicious homemade cooking.

Buyer

A VIKKOO.COM buyer is a customer with a hungry palate. Customers who seek that quintessential homemade cooking. Customers who wish to eat safe food. Customers who wish to not cook on a holiday.

Seller

VIKKOO.COM engages and partners with home chefs after various checks to ensure consistent quality food is prepared and delivered out of their kitchens. We follow an open-door policy as we stand hand-in-hand with our home chefs to teach and mentor them in ways of managing their online shop.
descriptionShort: VIKKOO.COM is designed to be an online platform to help home chefs.
